		<div id="comment_body_64128223">Are user reviews and ratings not a good enough pseudo 'human curation' system?

I don't think Steam already does this - but to improve this have reviews be restricted or can at least be filtered to those who are verified purchasers, and even better, to those who have played a minimum number of hours in a game.</div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64128223">
